title: CATFISHING: The Ghost of Easterville
description:
In the fall of 2011, a 17-year-old model struck up an online relationship with NBA player Chris “Birdman” Andersen. But someone else was pulling the strings of their ill-fated romance. This is our last crossover episode from the Crimes of Passion Valentine’s special. Follow Crimes of Passion for new episodes every week!
